Text: Thanks for the up! I can't believe it's been 20 years! I's old!
You're copyrighting your rips on the album artwork? What a joke.
Twenty years old and better than the vast majority of shit churned out today.

Congratulations! You're the 500th person to upload "Nevermind" to The Pirate Bay.

To hell with new content, I say! Let's just continually re-upload Nevermind, Led Zeppelin IV, Back In Black, and Dark Side Of The Moon!

I feel like I'm taking crazy pills....
